This project adapts evolutionary optimization concepts and is designed to work
with Google's Agent Development Kit (ADK). While gepa-adk is an independent
implementation, it draws inspiration from the GEPA framework's approach to
evolutionary prompt optimization.

For the complete list of dependencies and their licenses, see the
pyproject.toml file and the licenses included with each dependency.
